Package: nmarank
Title: Complex Hierarchy Questions in Network Meta-Analysis
Version: 0.3-0
Date: 2022-12-21
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0), meta (>= 5.5-0), netmeta (>= 2.5-0),
         data.tree, mvtnorm, tidyr
Imports: dplyr, tibble, rlang, MASS
Suggests: testthat
